channel.title: Name Suggestions
channel.description:
Hey guys, so I'm currently developing a Internet Web browser in Visual Basic. I am about 40% complete.
What I am posting this thread for is because I need [u]YOU[/u]to suggest some names for it, please don't post names of browsers that have already been made as they are most likely copy right, and I don't want to copy them either.
If a mod/admin has a problem with this thread, then feel free to go right ahead and lock it.

item.title: Name Suggestions
item.dc:creator: @kihomura Kihomura
item.description:
@kihomura wrote:

I’m horrible with names but I have some suggestions for you.

-Use C#, it’s much better for making applications
-Use the Gecko component to embed Firefox into your application, rather than Internet explorer
http://code.google.com/p/geckofx/

If I do think of some names I will come back and mention them.

Read full topic
